FTN::Log

Copyright (c) 2001-2006 Robert James Clay.  All Rights Reserved.
This is free software;  you can redistribute it and/or
modify it under the same terms as Perl itself.

Perl module for logging with/for fidonet/FTN processing.  

Various Log functions, including:

    logging($logfile, $id, $text)


For details, see documentation.

To install:
  Uncompress the archive, then change to that newly
created directory & do the following:

   1) perl Makefile.PL  
   2) make
   3) make test (optional)
   4) make install
   

